<h2>DHTML Calendar — for the impatient</h2>

      <blockquote>
        <p>
          This page demonstrates how to setup a flat calendar.  Examples of
          <em>popup</em> calendars are available in <a href="http://www.dynarch.com/demos/jscalendar/simple-1.html">another page</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          The code in this page uses a helper function defined in
          "calendar-setup.js".  With it you can setup the calendar in
          minutes.  If you're not <em>that</em> impatient, ;-) <a href="http://www.dynarch.com/demos/jscalendar/doc/html/reference.html">complete documenation</a> is
          available.
        </p>
      </blockquote>



